metadata.name: The Lich
metadata.description:
The Lich, Undead Lord of Lost Planks. 

A once beautiful Plank, its Driftwood Body slowly corrupted by foul and evil magicks. 
Aeons have passed since The Lich first turned to the darker paths of the Aether. 
It knows only The Hunger, forever gorging itself on the spirits of dead Planks. 

It is said that only the Heir of Jimmy can kill it.
